OL,3,CWales behind most European countries
OL,4,Cafter culture and sport cuts
OL,6,FYoung people are being "deprived of
OL,7,Fthe chance to explore their talents"
OL,8,Fas Wales lags behind other European
OL,9,Fcountries in sport and culture funding
OL,10,Fafter budget cuts, according to a new
OL,11,FSenedd Committee report.
OL,13,FThe report by the Senedd's Culture and
OL,14,FSport Committee shows that Wales ranks
OL,15,Fthird from bottom of European
OL,16,Fcountries in terms of spending per
OL,17,Fperson on recreational and sporting
OL,18,Fservices and second from bottom for
OL,19,Fcultural services.
