OL,3,CWales behind most European countries
OL,4,Cafter culture and sport cuts
OL,6,FAs well as detailing how "Wales risks
OL,7,Fbeing left behind in cultural and
OL,8,Fsporting achievement", the report
OL,9,Fcalls for action and increased funding
OL,10,Ffrom the Welsh Government and
OL,11,Fhighlights an urgent need for a
OL,12,Fstrategy.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government says it will be
OL,15,Fresponding to the committee's report
OL,16,Fand recommendations and criticised
OL,17,Fwhat they say have been "difficult
OL,18,Ffunding settlements from the UK
OL,19,FGovernment". They also said they would
OL,20,Fbe re-allocating funding for the
OL,21,Fsector in the draft 2025-26 budget.
