OL,3,CWales behind most European countries
OL,4,Cafter culture and sport cuts
OL,6,FThe report added that many sport and
OL,7,Fcultural venues across the UK are at
OL,8,Fthreat of closure as a result of cuts
OL,9,Fwith rising costs also adding pressure.
OL,11,FDelyth Jewell MS, Chair of the
OL,12,FCommittee said: "For too long, culture
OL,13,Fand sport have been treated as 'nice
OL,14,Fto haves,' facing relentless funding
OL,15,Freductions that have left these
OL,16,Fsectors brittle and under-resourced.
