OL,3,CWales behind most European countries
OL,4,Cafter culture and sport cuts
OL,6,F"The recent cuts in the 2024-25 Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment budget, compounded by
OL,8,Finflation and rising costs, have had a
OL,9,Fprofound impact. We must tackle this
OL,10,Fto ensure that spending per head on
OL,11,Fculture and sport becomes comparable
OL,12,Fwith other nations.
OL,14,F"Culture and sport are vital threads
OL,15,Fin the fabric of what makes life worth
OL,16,Fliving: they enrich the human
OL,17,Fexperience, and not merely luxuries to
OL,18,Fbe enjoyed during times of plenty.
