OL,3,CWales behind most European countries
OL,4,Cafter culture and sport cuts
OL,6,FThe report has made several
OL,7,Frecommendations to the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment, including increasing
OL,9,Ffunding on culture and sport until
OL,10,Fspending per head matches similar
OL,11,Fnations, introducing a preventative'
OL,12,Fcategory of spending in future budgets
OL,13,Fto recognise the value of culture and
OL,14,Fsport on physical and mental health,
OL,15,Fand ensuring culture and sport are
OL,16,Frecognised in key to achieving the
OL,17,Fgoals of the Well-being of Future
OL,18,FGenerations (Wales) Act 2015.
