OL,3,CWales behind most European countries
OL,4,Cafter culture and sport cuts
OL,6,FNia Wyn Evans from community theatre,
OL,7,FArad Goch said that rising costs
OL,8,Fcompounded by cuts have made it
OL,9,F"impossible to make ends meet".
OL,11,FShe said: "With the costs of
OL,12,Feverything such as wages, electricity,
OL,13,Ftravel costs and living costs
OL,14,Fincreasing so quickly, and the money
OL,15,Fcoming in staying the same or
OL,16,Fdecreasing - it's impossible to make
OL,17,Fends meet. There must be a compromise.
