OL,6,F"Our main aim as a company is to
OL,7,Fprovide theatre to as many children
OL,8,Fand young people as possible - but
OL,9,Fthese numbers are going to decrease
OL,10,Fdue to the length of our trips and our
OL,11,Fability to go to different locations.
