OL,3,CWales behind most European countries
OL,4,Cafter culture and sport cuts
OL,6,F"Wales' cultural, arts and sporting
OL,7,Fsectors make a vital social and
OL,8,Feconomic contribution to our society,
OL,9,Fenriching our communities and
OL,10,Finspiring future generations. We have,
OL,11,Fhowever, had to take very difficult
OL,12,Fdecisions to protect frontline
OL,13,Fservices following years of difficult
OL,14,Ffunding settlements from the UK
OL,15,FGovernment. The latest UK Government
OL,16,Fsettlement has provided an opportunity
OL,17,Ffor us to allocate increased funding
OL,18,Ffor our vital cultural, arts and
OL,19,Fsporting institutions in the draft
OL,20,F2025-26 budget."
